{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-template-js","path":"/pages/about/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"cccaa4bd-2560-5e2a-8089-354aa38cee3a","html":"<span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/6a068/profile.jpg\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source srcset=\"/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/8ac56/profile.webp 240w,\n/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/d3be9/profile.webp 480w,\n/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/e46b2/profile.webp 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/webp\">\n        <source srcset=\"/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/09b79/profile.jpg 240w,\n/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/7cc5e/profile.jpg 480w,\n/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/6a068/profile.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" type=\"image/jpeg\">\n        <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" src=\"/static/bbf4a5b13f9cb199fa599fd44e5794da/6a068/profile.jpg\" alt=\"profile\" title=\"profile\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\">\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<h2 id=\"안녕하세요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%88%EB%85%95%ED%95%98%EC%84%B8%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"안녕하세요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>안녕하세요</h2>\n<p>주니어 개발자입니다.\n음악과 춤, 고양이를 좋아합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"저는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%80%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"저는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>저는</h2>\n<p>개발하는데에 있어서 로직을 잘 짜는것도 좋지만, 커뮤니케이션이 많아야 한다고 믿습니다.\n능숙한 분야가 아니더라도 업무에 필요하다면 적극적으로 탐색하여 최적의 결과를 낼 수 있도록 노력하고 있습니다.\n주도적인 업무 환경을 선호합니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"앞으로\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%9E%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C\" aria-label=\"앞으로 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>앞으로</h2>\n<p>비즈니스의 가치를 높히는 개발자가 되는 것을 추구하고 있습니다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"skills\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#skills\" aria-label=\"skills permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Skills</h1>\n<h3 id=\"htmlcss\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#htmlcss\" aria-label=\"htmlcss permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTML/CSS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>시맨틱 마크업을 준수합니다.</li>\n<li>검색 엔진 최적화 경험이 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"python\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#python\" aria-label=\"python permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Python</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>파이썬 언어의 기본적인 문법에 대해 알고 있습니다.</li>\n<li>자료구조 및 알고리즘을 파이썬으로 공부했습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"tooling\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tooling\" aria-label=\"tooling permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tooling</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Git을 사용하며 Git Flow 등의 개발 방법론 경험이 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"devops\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#devops\" aria-label=\"devops permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>DevOps</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>AWS EC2, S3, RDS 등의 사용 경험이 있습니다.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"About me","date":null,"description":null,"socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/pages/about/"}}}